%% Pudel Authentication Flow vWorld Standard.group
%% OAuth2 + Optional DPoP Binding

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Vue as Vue Frontend
    participant API as Pudel API
    participant JWT as JWT Util (RSA)
    participant DPoP as DPoPService
    participant Discord as Discord OAuth2
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,DB: OAuth2 Login Flow (Standard or DPoP-Enhanced)

    User->>Vue: Click "Login with Discord"
    Vue->>Discord: Redirect to OAuth2 authorize
    Discord->>User: Show consent screen
    User->>Discord: Approve
    Discord->>Vue: Redirect with code

    Vue->>API: POST /api/auth/discord/callback
    Note right of Vue: Body: { code, redirectUri }<br/>Optional: DPoP header (proof JWT)

    API->>Discord: Exchange code for tokens
    Discord-->>API: access_token, refresh_token

    API->>Discord: GET /users/@me
    Discord-->>API: User info (id, username, avatar)

    API->>DB: Find or create user
    DB-->>API: User entity

    alt DPoP Header Present
        API->>DPoP: validateProofForTokenRequest(proof)
        DPoP-->>API: ✓ thumbprint
        API->>JWT: generateDPoPBoundToken(userId, claims, thumbprint)
        Note right of JWT: JWT contains cnf.jkt = thumbprint
        JWT-->>API: DPoP-bound JWT
        API->>DPoP: bindTokenToThumbprint(jwt, thumbprint)
        API-->>Vue: { token, user, token_type: "DPoP" }
    else No DPoP Header
        API->>JWT: generateToken(userId, claims)
        Note right of JWT: Standard Bearer JWT
        JWT-->>API: Signed JWT token
        API-->>Vue: { token, user, token_type: "Bearer" }
    end

    Vue->>Vue: Store token in localStorage

    Note over User,DB: Authenticated API Requests

    User->>Vue: View guilds

    alt Bearer Token
        Vue->>API: GET /api/guilds
        Note right of Vue: Authorization: Bearer <token>
    else DPoP Token
        Vue->>Vue: Create fresh DPoP proof
        Vue->>API: GET /api/guilds
        Note right of Vue: Authorization: DPoP <token><br/>DPoP: <fresh proof JWT>
    end

    API->>JWT: Validate JWT (RSA public key)
    JWT-->>API: Valid / Invalid

    alt Token Valid
        API->>DB: Query user's guilds
        DB-->>API: Guild list
        API-->>Vue: { guilds: [...] }
        Vue-->>User: Display guilds
    else Token Invalid/Expired
        API-->>Vue: 401 Unauthorized
        Vue->>Vue: Redirect to login
    end

    Note over User,DB: Logout

    Vue->>API: POST /api/auth/logout
    Note right of Vue: Authorization: Bearer/DPoP <token>
    API->>DPoP: revokeTokenBinding(token)
    API-->>Vue: 200 OK
